{"tid":1403354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）點樣可以神回班垃圾 ,文宣請進","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:48:05.000Z","uid":230892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64a5f0f2fd9765fd4492ff001d586549d7930197","tid":1403354,"uid":230892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:38:59.000Z","msg":"呢一個月，同好多親戚、藍絲、港豬、大陸人、新移民哎過好多次，想集思廣益，諗一套神回圖，點樣一句或者一個問題令到佢駁唔到或者會<span style=\"color: red;\">認真反思</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n我唔想哎交、因為哎完係得唔到更多人支持，<br />\n我想改變到佢地少少諗法，都好呀...<br />\n<br />\n通常我遇到都係呢幾句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 搞事系列：</span></span><br />\n-好暴力呀 <br />\n-比你地呢人搞到亂曬 <br />\n-而家搞到民生啦！<br />\n-香港玩完啦，個市大跌，鋪頭又關曬門<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 陰謀系列： </span></span><br />\n-成班比人利用都唔知 <br />\n-佢地係咪收左錢？ <br />\n-聽講係有班有錢佬係背後支持 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 港豬系列： </span></span><br />\n- 我覺得唔關我事 <br />\n-我地呢D人唔識我咁多..<br />\n-我不嬲唔理政治<br />\n-搞掂自己先啦<br />\n<br />\n我見網上有幾張唔錯，想要多d<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYE4V13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYE4V13.png&h=4b27e167&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VbTUyOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVbTUyOQ.png&h=3d2ad231&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83h968V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83h968V.png&h=142b623e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29e72a5e84240929822eadd0fa49977390db7181","tid":1403354,"uid":230892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:40:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cb1300591d061a3f4618fe2c36157b2860eee5b","tid":1403354,"uid":230892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:43:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"944528715adac71a7b634a924959359a1ccd27d1","tid":1403354,"uid":230892,"like":0,"dislike":